### Connect and send a "message" event on connect
WEBSOCKET ws://localhost:8082/api/ws
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "event_type": "message",
  "payload": {
    "private_id": 1,
    "receiver_id": 3,
    "message_type": "text",
    "content": "hello from kulala"
  }
}

